    "English": "An exclusive placeable decal, to add flair and decoration to bases.<br>This <span class=\"name name-special\">cursed</span> decal depicts the mighty <span class=\"name name-stellar\">titan worm</span>.<br><br>\"The veins of the Atlas had surfaced.\"",
